   "source": [
    "### 模型拆分推理（Split Computing）\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 什么是模型拆分推理？\n",
    "\n",
    "将$L$层模型分为端侧$L_e$层和云端$L_c$层，端侧执行前半部分，中间特征上传云端，云端执行后半部分并返回结果。\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 为什么用模型拆分推理？\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **端侧算力不足**：端侧设备无法运行完整大模型，但可以运行前几层\n",
    "2. **隐私保护**：原始数据不上传云端，仅上传中间特征（不可逆）\n",
    "3. **带宽节省**：中间特征可量化压缩后传输\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 模型拆分的数学原理\n",
    "\n",
    "拆分点选择：\n",
    "$$l^* = \\arg\\min_l (T_{\\text{edge}}(l) + T_{\\text{transfer}}(l) + T_{\\text{cloud}}(l))$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $T_{\\text{edge}}(l)$：端侧执行前$l$层的延迟\n",
    "- $T_{\\text{transfer}}(l)$：传输中间特征的延迟$= \\frac{|h_l| \\cdot d}{\\text{BW}} + T_{\\text{latency}}$\n",
    "- $T_{\\text{cloud}}(l)$：云端执行后$L-l$层的延迟\n",
    "- $|h_l| \\cdot d$：第$l$层输出的数据量（序列长度$\\times$隐藏维度$\\times$元素字节数）\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 中间特征压缩\n",
    "\n",
    "中间特征$h_l \\in \\mathbb{R}^{L_{\\text{seq}} \\times d_{\\text{hidden}}}$的传输量：\n",
    "- FP32：$L_{\\text{seq}} \\times d_{\\text{hidden}} \\times 4$ bytes\n",
    "- FP16量化：传输量减半，精度损失可忽略\n",
    "- INT8量化：传输量降至1/4，需校准量化参数\n",
    "- 特征蒸馏：训练小型投影头将$d_{\\text{hidden}}$压缩到$d_{\\text{compact}}$\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 隐私增强\n",
    "\n",
    "中间特征并非完全不可逆，攻击者可能通过反演攻击重建输入。增强隐私的方法：\n",
    "- **噪声注入**：$h'_l = h_l + \\epsilon, \\epsilon \\sim \\mathcal{N}(0, \\sigma^2 I)$，牺牲少量精度\n",
    "- **特征扰动**：随机丢弃部分特征维度\n",
    "- **加密传输**：TLS 1.3加密中间特征，防止中间人攻击"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class SplitPoint(Enum):\n",
    "    EARLY = 'early'\n",
    "    MIDDLE = 'middle'\n",
    "    LATE = 'late'\n",
    "\n",
    "class IntermediateFeatureCompressor:\n",
    "    \"\"\"中间特征压缩器: 量化+可选噪声注入\"\"\"\n",
    "    def __init__(self, quant_dtype='fp16', noise_sigma=0.0):\n",
    "        self.quant_dtype = quant_dtype\n",
    "        self.noise_sigma = noise_sigma\n",
    "\n",
    "    def compress(self, feature: torch.Tensor) -> Tuple[torch.Tensor, Dict]:\n",
    "        metadata = {'original_dtype': str(feature.dtype), 'original_shape': feature.shape}\n",
    "        if self.noise_sigma > 0:\n",
    "            noise = torch.randn_like(feature) * self.noise_sigma\n",
    "            feature = feature + noise\n",
    "            metadata['noise_injected'] = True\n",
    "        if self.quant_dtype == 'fp16':\n",
    "            compressed = feature.half()\n",
    "        elif self.quant_dtype == 'int8':\n",
    "            scale = feature.abs().max(dim=-1, keepdim=True).values / 127.0\n",
    "            scale = scale.clamp(min=1e-8)\n",
    "            compressed = (feature / scale).round().clamp(-128, 127).to(torch.int8)\n",
    "            metadata['scale'] = scale\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            compressed = feature\n",
    "        metadata['compressed_dtype'] = str(compressed.dtype)\n",
    "        metadata['compressed_bytes'] = compressed.numel() * compressed.element_size()\n",
    "        return compressed, metadata\n",
    "\n",
    "    def decompress(self, compressed: torch.Tensor, metadata: Dict) -> torch.Tensor:\n",
    "        if self.quant_dtype == 'int8' and 'scale' in metadata:\n",
    "            return compressed.float() * metadata['scale']\n",
    "        elif self.quant_dtype == 'fp16':\n",
    "            return compressed.float()\n",
    "        return compressed\n",
    "\n",
    "class SplitTransformer(nn.Module):\n",
    "    \"\"\"可拆分的Transformer，支持产业级中间特征压缩\"\"\"\n",
    "    def __init__(self, dim=64, n_layers=6, n_heads=4, split_point=3):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.split_point = split_point\n",
    "        self.n_layers = n_layers\n",
    "        self.edge_layers = nn.ModuleList([\n",
    "            nn.TransformerEncoderLayer(d_model=dim, nhead=n_heads, batch_first=True)\n",
    "            for _ in range(split_point)\n",
    "        ])\n",
    "        self.cloud_layers = nn.ModuleList([\n",
    "            nn.TransformerEncoderLayer(d_model=dim, nhead=n_heads, batch_first=True)\n",
    "            for _ in range(split_point, n_layers)\n",
    "        ])\n",
    "        self.compressor = IntermediateFeatureCompressor(quant_dtype='fp16', noise_sigma=0.0)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def edge_forward(self, x):\n",
    "        for layer in self.edge_layers:\n",
    "            x = layer(x)\n",
    "        return x\n",
    "\n",
    "    def cloud_forward(self, x):\n",
    "        for layer in self.cloud_layers:\n",
    "            x = layer(x)\n",
    "        return x\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x, simulate_transfer=False):\n",
    "        x = self.edge_forward(x)\n",
    "        if simulate_transfer:\n",
    "            compressed, meta = self.compressor.compress(x)\n",
    "            x = self.compressor.decompress(compressed, meta)\n",
    "        x = self.cloud_forward(x)\n",
    "        return x\n",
    "\n",
    "dim, n_layers, n_heads = 64, 6, 4\n",
    "model = SplitTransformer(dim, n_layers, n_heads, split_point=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "edge_params = sum(p.numel() for p in model.edge_layers.parameters())\n",
    "cloud_params = sum(p.numel() for p in model.cloud_layers.parameters())\n",
    "total_params = edge_params + cloud_params\n",
    "\n",
    "x = torch.randn(2, 16, dim)\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "    intermediate = model.edge_forward(x)\n",
    "    final_no_compress = model.cloud_forward(intermediate)\n",
    "    final_with_compress = model(x, simulate_transfer=True)\n",
    "    full = model(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "compress_diff = (final_no_compress - final_with_compress).abs().max().item()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"=== 模型拆分推理 ===\")\n",
    "print(f\"总层数: {n_layers}, 拆分点: 第{3}层\")\n",
    "print(f\"端侧参数: {edge_params:,} ({edge_params/total_params:.1%})\")\n",
    "print(f\"云端参数: {cloud_params:,} ({cloud_params/total_params:.1%})\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n--- 中间特征压缩对比 ---\")\n",
    "for dtype_name, dtype_bytes in [('FP32', 4), ('FP16', 2), ('INT8', 1)]:\n",
    "    transfer_bytes = intermediate.numel() * dtype_bytes\n",
    "    print(f\"  {dtype_name}: {transfer_bytes/1024:.2f} KB\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n--- FP16压缩传输的精度影响 ---\")\n",
    "print(f\"  压缩前后最大差异: {compress_diff:.8f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  结论: FP16压缩几乎无损，是产业级标配\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n--- 网络传输延迟估算 ---\")\n",
    "networks = [\n",
    "    ('WiFi 6', 1.2e9, 5e-3),\n",
    "    ('5G', 100e6, 15e-3),\n",
    "    ('4G LTE', 20e6, 50e-3),\n",
    "]\n",
    "fp16_bytes = intermediate.numel() * 2\n",
    "for net_name, bw, latency in networks:\n",
    "    transfer_time = fp16_bytes * 8 / bw + latency\n",
    "    print(f\"  {net_name}: FP16传输={transfer_time*1000:.1f}ms\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n隐私保护: 上传中间特征而非原始输入，云端无法直接还原原始数据\")\n",
    "print(f"增强隐私: 可对中间特征添加噪声(σ>0)或使用TLS加密传输\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
