   "source": [
    "### 自适应推理路由\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 什么是自适应推理路由？\n",
    "\n",
    "根据输入复杂度动态决定请求在端侧还是云端处理。简单请求端侧处理（低延迟），复杂请求卸载到云端（高精度）。\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 为什么需要自适应路由？\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **请求复杂度不均**：简单请求（闲聊）端侧即可处理，复杂请求（推理、创作）需要云端大模型\n",
    "2. **成本优化**：减少不必要的云端API调用\n",
    "3. **延迟优化**：简单请求避免网络往返延迟\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 自适应路由的数学原理\n",
    "\n",
    "路由决策：\n",
    "$$\\text{route}(x) = \\begin{cases} \\text{edge} & \\text{if } \\text{conf}(f_{\\text{edge}}(x)) > \\tau \\\\ \\text{cloud} & \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $\\text{conf}(f_{\\text{edge}}(x))$：端侧模型的预测置信度\n",
    "- $\\tau$：置信度阈值，控制端侧处理比例\n",
    "- 端侧处理比例$\\rho = P(\\text{conf} > \\tau)$，越大则云端负载越低\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 产业级路由策略\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **置信度路由**：端侧模型输出softmax最大概率作为置信度\n",
    "2. **复杂度估计路由**：轻量级分类器预测输入复杂度（token数、语义复杂度）\n",
    "3. **多阈值路由**：不同任务类型使用不同阈值（翻译$\\tau_1$、摘要$\\tau_2$、推理$\\tau_3$）\n",
    "4. **级联路由**：端侧先尝试，低置信度时再请求云端（带缓存）\n",
    "5. **A/B测试**：线上实验确定最优阈值，平衡端侧处理率和准确率"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "@dataclass\n",
    "class RoutingRequest:\n",
    "    request_id: str\n",
    "    input_tokens: int\n",
    "    task_type: str\n",
    "    embedding: torch.Tensor\n",
    "    privacy_level: str = 'normal'\n",
    "\n",
    "@dataclass\n",
    "class RoutingDecision:\n",
    "    request_id: str\n",
    "    target: str\n",
    "    confidence: float\n",
    "    reason: str\n",
    "    latency_estimate_ms: float\n",
    "    cost_estimate_usd: float\n",
    "\n",
    "class AdaptiveInferenceRouter:\n",
    "    \"\"\"产业级自适应推理路由器\n",
    "    综合考虑: 输入复杂度、任务类型、隐私等级、网络条件\"\"\"\n",
    "    TASK_THRESHOLDS = {\n",
    "        'chat': 0.4,\n",
    "        'translation': 0.5,\n",
    "        'summarization': 0.6,\n",
    "        'reasoning': 0.7,\n",
    "        'creative_writing': 0.8,\n",
    "    }\n",
    "\n",
    "    EDGE_COST_PER_REQ = 0.0\n",
    "    CLOUD_COST_PER_REQ = 0.002\n",
    "    EDGE_LATENCY_MS = 50\n",
    "    CLOUD_LATENCY_MS = 300\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __init__(self, edge_model, cloud_model, default_threshold=0.5):\n",
    "        self.edge_model = edge_model\n",
    "        self.cloud_model = cloud_model\n",
    "        self.default_threshold = default_threshold\n",
    "        self.complexity_head = nn.Linear(64, 1)\n",
    "        self.routing_stats = {'edge': 0, 'cloud': 0, 'privacy_override': 0}\n",
    "\n",
    "    def _estimate_input_complexity(self, req: RoutingRequest) -> float:\n",
    "        \"\"\"基于多维度启发式估计输入复杂度\"\"\"\n",
    "        with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "            feat = req.embedding.mean(dim=1) if req.embedding.dim() == 3 else req.embedding\n",
    "            model_score = torch.sigmoid(self.complexity_head(feat)).squeeze().item()\n",
    "        length_score = min(req.input_tokens / 512.0, 1.0)\n",
    "        task_complexity = {\n",
    "            'chat': 0.2, 'translation': 0.3, 'summarization': 0.5,\n",
    "            'reasoning': 0.8, 'creative_writing': 0.9\n",
    "        }.get(req.task_type, 0.5)\n",
    "        complexity = 0.3 * model_score + 0.3 * length_score + 0.4 * task_complexity\n",
    "        return complexity\n",
    "\n",
    "    def route(self, req: RoutingRequest) -> RoutingDecision:\n",
    "        \"\"\"路由决策: 综合复杂度、隐私、任务类型\"\"\"\n",
    "        if req.privacy_level == 'sensitive':\n",
    "            self.routing_stats['privacy_override'] += 1\n",
    "            return RoutingDecision(\n",
    "                request_id=req.request_id, target='edge',\n",
    "                confidence=1.0, reason='privacy_override',\n",
    "                latency_estimate_ms=self.EDGE_LATENCY_MS,\n",
    "                cost_estimate_usd=self.EDGE_COST_PER_REQ\n",
    "            )\n",
    "\n",
    "        complexity = self._estimate_input_complexity(req)\n",
    "        threshold = self.TASK_THRESHOLDS.get(req.task_type, self.default_threshold)\n",
    "\n",
    "        if complexity < threshold:\n",
    "            target = 'edge'\n",
    "            self.routing_stats['edge'] += 1\n",
    "            reason = f'complexity={complexity:.2f} < threshold={threshold}'\n",
    "            latency = self.EDGE_LATENCY_MS\n",
    "            cost = self.EDGE_COST_PER_REQ\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            target = 'cloud'\n",
    "            self.routing_stats['cloud'] += 1\n",
    "            reason = f'complexity={complexity:.2f} >= threshold={threshold}'\n",
    "            latency = self.CLOUD_LATENCY_MS\n",
    "            cost = self.CLOUD_COST_PER_REQ\n",
    "\n",
    "        return RoutingDecision(\n",
    "            request_id=req.request_id, target=target,\n",
    "            confidence=1.0 - abs(complexity - threshold),\n",
    "            reason=reason, latency_estimate_ms=latency, cost_estimate_usd=cost\n",
    "        )\n",
    "\n",
    "    def route_batch(self, requests: List[RoutingRequest]) -> List[RoutingDecision]:\n",
    "        return [self.route(req) for req in requests]\n",
    "\n",
    "edge_model = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(64, 32), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(32, 64))\n",
    "cloud_model = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "    nn.Linear(64, 128), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(128, 64),\n",
    "    nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(64, 64)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "router = AdaptiveInferenceRouter(edge_model, cloud_model, default_threshold=0.5)\n",
    "\n",
    "test_requests = [\n",
    "    RoutingRequest('req_001', input_tokens=20, task_type='chat',\n",
    "                   embedding=torch.randn(1, 4, 64), privacy_level='normal'),\n",
    "    RoutingRequest('req_002', input_tokens=500, task_type='reasoning',\n",
    "                   embedding=torch.randn(1, 8, 64), privacy_level='normal'),\n",
    "    RoutingRequest('req_003', input_tokens=100, task_type='translation',\n",
    "                   embedding=torch.randn(1, 4, 64), privacy_level='sensitive'),\n",
    "    RoutingRequest('req_004', input_tokens=300, task_type='creative_writing',\n",
    "                   embedding=torch.randn(1, 6, 64), privacy_level='normal'),\n",
    "    RoutingRequest('req_005', input_tokens=50, task_type='summarization',\n",
    "                   embedding=torch.randn(1, 3, 64), privacy_level='normal'),\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "decisions = router.route_batch(test_requests)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"=== 自适应推理路由 ===\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n{'请求ID':<10} {'任务类型':<15} {'Token数':<8} {'隐私':<8} {'路由':<6} {'原因'}\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 70)\n",
    "for req, dec in zip(test_requests, decisions):\n",
    "    print(f\"{req.request_id:<10} {req.task_type:<15} {req.input_tokens:<8} \"\n",
    "          f\"{req.privacy_level:<8} {dec.target:<6} {dec.reason}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n--- 路由统计 ---\")\n",
    "total = sum(router.routing_stats.values())\n",
    "for key, val in router.routing_stats.items():\n",
    "    print(f\"  {key}: {val} ({val/total:.0%})\")\n",
    "\n",
